data.description: Welcome to The Haven.  This lovely corner lot home is approximately 1800 sf with 4 beds and 2 baths on a 1/2 acre lot.  A wood fence encompasses the large backyard to offer privacy and security. The front boasts attractive landscaping, a long double car driveway and 2 car garage. Some interior features include a gas log fireplace, built-in bookshelves in the living room, kitchen pantry, granite countertops, whirlpool tub, and walk-in closet.  The entire interior also has a fresh paint job. Give Lisa Eakins a call for more info or to schedule a tour, 580-678-3774.
